      <title>官员警告称，英国基金因国内投资不足面临税收风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-24/uk-funds-risk-tax-hit-for-underinvesting-at-home-official-warns</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国商业银行行长在警告称，在政府推行一项关键增长计划之际，英国可能会向未能在国内进行足够投资的资产管理公司收回养老金税收减免。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-24/uk-funds-risk-tax-hit-for-underinvesting-at-home-official-warns</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 24 Nov 2024 06:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>警方称，泰国医疗大亨因诈骗被通缉，现已逃往中国</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-24/thai-medical-tycoon-wanted-for-fraud-fled-to-china-police-say</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国医院大亨 Boon Vanasin 通过虚假医疗项目骗取了约 75 亿泰铢（2.17 亿美元）的投资，现已逃往中国，警方随即对其发出了逮捕令。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-24/thai-medical-tycoon-wanted-for-fraud-fled-to-china-police-say</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 24 Nov 2024 04:59:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿达尼被美国证券交易委员会传唤解释贿赂案立场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-24/adani-summoned-by-us-sec-to-explain-position-in-bribery-case</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据印度报业托拉斯报道，印度亿万富翁高塔姆阿达尼和他的侄子萨加尔阿达尼被美国证券交易委员会传唤，解释他们为赢得太阳能合同而支付了超过 2.5 亿美元的贿赂的指控。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-24/adani-summoned-by-us-sec-to-explain-position-in-bribery-case</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 24 Nov 2024 04:41:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿达尼贿赂案将如何考验美国法律的长臂</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-24/how-adani-bribe-case-will-test-the-long-arm-of-us-law</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国检察官在试图监禁亿万富翁高塔姆·阿达尼 (Gautam Adani) 时面临严峻的法律和外交障碍，他涉嫌帮助策划向印度官员行贿超过 2.5 亿美元并欺骗美国投资者。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-24/how-adani-bribe-case-will-test-the-long-arm-of-us-law</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 24 Nov 2024 03:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
